-- Mortgage insurer Genworth Financial profit rises 79 pct
-- By Avik Das in Bangalore
-- Tue Apr 29, 2014 05:21PM EDT
-- None



April 29 (Reuters) - Genworth Financial Inc <GNW.N> reported a 79 percent rise in quarterly profit helped by higher income from its global mortgage insurance and U.S. life insurance businesses.

Net income rose to $184 million, or 37 cents per share, in the first quarter ended March 31, from $103 million, or 21 cents per share, a year earlier. [ID:nPn4cPVVp]